-sep text-sep-comment'>/</span><span class="blog-categories minor-meta">in <a href="https://blog.darwinex.com/category/opinion-editorial-es/?lang=es" rel="tag">POSTS</a> </span><span class="text-sep text-sep-cat">/</span><span class="blog-author minor-meta">by <span class="entry-author-link" itemprop="name"><span class="vcard author"><span class="fn"><a href="https://blog.darwinex.com/author/the-market-owl/?lang=es" title="Posts by The Market Owl" rel="author">The Market Owl</a></span></span></span></span></span></header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">¬°Ya es oficial! </span></p>
<p>La ESMA ha publicado las nuevas normas aplicables tanto a traders como a proveedores de<span style="font-weight: 400;">¬†<em>Contracts for Differences</em> (o CFDs) y <em>forex </em>(o FX). </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">En el presente art√≠culo revisaremos la s nuevas medidas y analizaremos las consecuencias para:</span></p>
<ol>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Darwinex</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Inversores en DARWINS</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Proveedores de DARWINS (es decir, traders)</span>
<ol>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Invertibles</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;">No invertibles (todav√≠a)</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Brokers &amp; Broker-dealers</span></li>
</ol>
<hr />
<p><span class="hs-cta-wrapper" id="hs-cta-wrapper-ce18872f-289f-4d1f-9254-975868954810"><span class="hs-cta-node hs-cta-ce18872f-289f-4d1f-9254-975868954810" id="hs-cta-ce18872f-289f-4d1f-9254-975868954810"><!--[if lte IE 8]>

